  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2023-03-09",
    "date": "2023-06-09T21:24:25Z",
    "text": "Advisory Committees Free of ESG Act of 2023\n\nThis bill prohibits the establishment of federal advisory committees on the basis of environmental, social, and governance aspects and provides for the termination of any existing advisory committees authorized or implemented on such basis.\n\nAdditionally, the bill authorizes civil actions seeking a determination that an advisory committee was authorized, permitted, or implemented in violation of such provision. The court must order any such advisory committee to be terminated immediately upon such determination."
